        "content": "<p>Is it possible to have a channel where users can share anything they stumble upon as a nice trick to work more efficiently with Isabelle. e.g. to prove that a locale is inconsistent, it seems like <code>lemma foo: False</code> and <code>sledgehammer</code> are a nice starting point</p>",
        "id": 580733040,
        "sender_full_name": "Ant S.",
        "timestamp": 1774035098
    },
