        "content": "<p>This topic was moved here from <a href=\"#narrow/channel/238552-Beginner-Questions/topic/.5Bmeta.5D.20an.20advice.20channel.20for.20tips.2Ftricks.20we.20may.20stumble.20upon\">#Beginner Questions &gt; &#91;meta&#93; an advice channel for tips/tricks we may stumble upon</a> by <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"233154\">Kevin Kappelmann</span>.</p>",
